FSM P1Mothership

States Hide, Amble, Retreat, GetIntoPosition, InPosition, DefendYourself, BackInPosition, PatrolPlayerFleet, Retreat2,
       OuttaHereLikeVladimir, HyperspaceOut, NullState;

    INIT
